{"article_id":"lpbLKWW6b9dlFGs2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Fewer people are now in favor of the Green New Deal","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"and the disappointment of The Washington Post was palpable .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"It turned out that","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"once more people knew more about the socialist fantasy","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to save the planet","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"( and give away a bunch of other stuff ) ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"attitudes shifted against it .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"To the Post this was proof","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"the \" GOP campaign \"","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"to \" sour the plan in the minds of Republican voters \"","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"was working .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"\" New polling from Yale and George Mason universities suggests","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that support for that climate plan from prominent freshman congresswomen Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"( D-N.Y. )","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"dropped steeply among Republicans over the past four months","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"since she and other lawmakers formally introduced it in February , \"","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"the Post wrote on May 10 .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"It couldn ' t possibly be that","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"by knowing more about a Green New Deal","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"than a \" description of its aspirations \" had persuaded people against it .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The Post insisted on May 10 ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"it was the Republicans and Fox News messaging against it .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"The \" PowerPost \" analysis by reporter Dino Grandoni also covered up for the embarrassing summary document","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"released by Ocasio-Cortez ' office with the Green New Deal resolution .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"Grandoni claimed","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"a \" tsunami of dissent came","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"even though Ocasio-Cortez ' resolution does not mention","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" banning hamburgers , air travel or ice cream . \"","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Instead , an erroneous summary of the Green New Deal","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"published by her office ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"but then retracted ,","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"mentioned eventually wanting to get rid of ' farting cows and airplanes , ' \"","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"he wrote .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Yes , her office did retract a FAQ sheet","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"claiming","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"it was \" incomplete \"","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"and \" published by accident , \"","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"but even The New York Times recognized","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"this was backpedaling over the major \" flub. \"","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"The rollout was so bad ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"an adviser to Ocasio-Cortez falsely suggested","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"the document was misinformation from political opponents","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"before the document was scrubbed from her website .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"There ' s was no reason","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"to think","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"the FAQ didn ' t include accurate sentiments or goals of her staff regarding the Green New Deal .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"Would it have been retracted","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"if no one had objected","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"( or noticed )","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"the document","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"containing socialist promises of guaranteed jobs , education , \" access to nature , \" \" healthy food , \" health care , housing , \" economic security for all","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"who are unable or unwilling to work \" and more ?","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"building \" high-speed rail at a scale","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"where air travel stops becoming necessary \"","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"\" Ensure that all GND jobs are union jobs","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"that pay prevailing wages","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"and hire local \"","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Fox wasn ' t the only media critical of the plan .","depth":3},{"id":58,"text":"Bloomberg opinion columnist Noah Smith called it \" unaffordable \"","depth":4},{"id":59,"text":"even before including \" all of the promises","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"listed in the FAQ . \"","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"Grandoni admitted","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"the original polling from George Mason \" did not include any mention of the possible costs , \"","depth":5},{"id":63,"text":"but he didn ' t suggest","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"that might have produced an inflated sense of support for a Green New Deal .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"As for those costs , he said","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"cost estimates from \" conservative \" groups were up to $ 100 trillion ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"but undermined the estimates","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"\" supporters of the plan \" called them \" misleading . \"","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"The Post ' s skewed analysis was in line with other liberal media","depth":4},{"id":71,"text":"which either ignored the kooky resolution","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"or tried to portray it as popular .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":145,"left":129,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":94,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":79,"right":93,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":74,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":2,"right":77,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":77,"left":76,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":3,"right":75,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"paren